==开发==
{{NotChineseSect}}
2013年4月25日，該產品的遊戲截圖被泄漏。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://simsvip.com/2013/04/25/the-sims-4-pre-production-ui-design-screens/|title="The Sims 4" Pre-Production UI Design Screens|date=2013-04-25|publisher=SimsVIP|accessdate=2013-05-11|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422033608/http://simsvip.com/2013/04/25/the-sims-4-pre-production-ui-design-screens/|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月3日，美商藝電傳送了電郵給數個非官方網站，說在5月6日將會有大宣佈，部分人猜測該宣佈是關於《模擬市民4》。<ref name="ea">{{cite web | url=http://www.ea.com/news/maxis-unveils-the-sims-4 | title=Maxis Unveils The Sims 4 | publisher=[[Electronic_Arts|Electronic Arts]] | date=2013-05-06 | accessdate=2013-05-06 | archive-date=2016-04-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414054850/http://www.ea.com/news/maxis-unveils-the-sims-4 | dead-url=no }}</ref>同日，TheSims4.com域名啓用，並把網址重定向至《模擬市民》的官方網站<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thesims4.com/|title=The Sims 4|publisher=Electronic Arts|accessdate=2013-05-06|archive-date=2019-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190918221555/https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

除了研發《模擬市民3》的[[The_Sims_Studio|模擬市民工作室]]，[[Maxis|Maxis]]也會加入《模擬市民4》的研發。由於最近[[Maxis|Maxis]]在研發《[[模拟城市_(2013年电子游戏)|模擬城市（2013）]]》，這標誌着Maxis將回歸[[模拟人生系列|《模擬市民》系列]]。

《模擬市民4》是單人遊戲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ea.com/news/the-sims-4-in-development-for-pc-and-mac|title=The Sims 4 in development for pc and mac|publisher=Electronic Arts|accessdate=2013-05-06|archive-date=2015-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151221170539/http://www.ea.com/news/the-sims-4-in-development-for-pc-and-mac|dead-url=no}}</ref>，故不需像[[模拟城市_(2013年电子游戏)|模擬城市]]般需要網絡連線才可遊玩<ref>{{cite news| url= http://www.3news.co.nz/The-Sims-4-announced/tabid/418/articleID/296807/Default.aspx |work=3 News NZ |title= Sims 4 announced | date=2013-05-07}}</ref>。

